        "desc": "",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/10/157749474/728c09491c76cf0d07a0d182e8fd9795_5615328872873370396.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
