        "desc": "",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/10/157749474/84798569350b3d70ebb96f57caaad016_1614440255556146765.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
        "type": "Heading",
        "level": 2,
        "text": "玛丽安纪念公园",
        "alignment": "center"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomImage",
        "url": "https:/act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/07/288375639/9313055236b1636d284df12e96857fa6_1188714990764422768.png",
        "alignment": "left"
      },
      {
        "type": "RichText",
        "text": "一个专门为阿兰·吉约丹的妹妹玛丽安·吉约丹而建的公园。下面是博絮埃的水下实验室。\n<color=#ffe699>相关词条：</color>"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 3979,
        "desc": "",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 4603,
        "name": "阿兰·吉约丹",
        "desc": "<p>埃马纽艾尔・吉约丹的养子，与他的养姐玛丽安一起在水仙十字院长大。他是枫丹动能工程科学研究院的创始人，他在枫丹最显著的贡献是他在芒性与荒性方面的研究，这也导向了始基力系统的发明和发条机关的创造。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyowiki/2023/12/08/5f9666801f8c3cd059ac14e8eb9dbc96_7678703120881801935.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 4602,
        "name": "玛丽安·吉约丹",
        "desc": "<p><span>埃马纽艾尔·吉约丹的养女，与哥哥阿兰在水仙十字院长大。</span></p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/06/157749474/7f04e9d0b83ab550cc91ddf708008a7d_4703821637585920261.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
